..�A strange image has been burned into your mind.
..�Oh, thanks for coming. Well, let's start by checking any suspicious-looking place we can find.
1�You really came! Let's go! Hurry! Let's check out anything that looks out of place!
1�Hm...I've seen this strange place a few times already now, but what could it possibly be?
1�What in Vana'diel is this made of? I have a feeling we should check this out...
1�What is this? Maybe if we examine it, we'll get some kind of hint...
1�Something is definitely weird here! Let's check it out!
1�Something from outside made it in here!? Let's check it out!
1�There's something weird about this place! I can see it perfectly, but it somehow looks hazy! Let's check it out!
1�What's this...? The scenery looks familiar, but kind of creepy...
1�...Something from outside? Maybe not. It seems the same as everything else here.
1�The outside world is somehow being reflected in this? Strange...
1�What could this be? The outside world appears to be reflected in it.
1�There is something here. Is this not from outside? How did it come to be in such a place?
1�Everything here seems to be made of a peculiar substance. Let us find out as much about it as possible.
1�What is this? Why are some spots clear, and others are not?
1�I've seen this before in the Emptiness... What could it be? Strange, isn't it?
1�There's something here. I'm not sure what it is, but I think we should check it out. Or rather I should say, I'm not sure what it is, and that's why we should check it out!
1�Hm? This looks like...the outside world!? It looks like it, but it's different somehow! How could that be?
1�Everything here is so creepy! I can't figure out if things in front of me are real or not! I don't get it at all!
1�Hmmm! What could this be? Let's find out!

1�There is something here. Is this not from outside? How did it come to be in such a place?

1�What could this be? I think it might be worth checking.
1�Wh...what's this...? The scenary looks strangely familiar...
1�Isn't this something from outside...or not? What could it be...?
1�Now, what substance could this possibly be made from? Let's take a closer look, shall we?
1�A truly disturbing sight. It's as though parts of our world have been ripped out and left here in this darkness...

1�Hmmm... I've never seen anything like it before. This warrants close examination.
1�Anyway, we've learned all we can here. Want to go now?

1�We've collected enough information, don't you think? Time to head back?
